The title of '''Crypt Master''' was given to those [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustans]] who maintained the burial vaults on their homeworld of [[Sullust/Legends|Sullust]]. In addition to this role, they also presided over the [[Tomb-walling ceremony|tomb-walling ceremonies]].

